name: WILDMTCH.WAD
description: OK Deathmatch lovers. Here it is !!! I've played alot of deathmatches so I knew what I wanted. It's not so big ya spend all day looking for each other. It's in an arena format where 2-4 people can chase each other around for hours and never get bored. Lots of places to hide and ambush. Also fun coop and alone. A must have !!
